 station 31045 via station 31042 (the first ride is from station 31042 back
 to station 31042); 
\begin_inset Formula $M_{2,3}M_{3,5}$
\end_inset

 represents the percentage of bikes at station 31042 that are destined for
 station 31045 via station 31043; and so on.
